Class Description
ActivationStrategy
Represents the different methods of activating VeinMiner.
AlgorithmConfig
Represents various configurable options for the vein miner algorithm.
AntiCheatHook
Represents a hook for an anticheat plugin.
AntiCheatHookAAC
The default Advanced AntiCheat (AAC) hook implementation
AntiCheatHookAntiAura
The default AntiAura hook implementation
AntiCheatHookNCP
The default NoCheatPlus (NCP) hook implementation
AntiCheatHookSpartan
The default Spartan hook implementation
BlockList
Represents a list of blocks and states (see VeinBlock).
ConfigWrapper  
EconomyModifier
A wrapper for economic transactions provided either by a vault based economy or a custom one supplied by another plugin.
EmptyEconomyModifier
An implementation of EconomyModifier with no affect on the player.
ItemValidator
A utility class that acts as a medium for checking the validity of items and materials.
MaterialAlias
Represents an aliasing between multiple VeinBlocks which VeinMiner can recognise as a single material value when being vein mined.
NonNullHashSet<T>
A more specific implementation of HashSet that prevents the addition of null values.
Pair<L,​R>
Represents a pair of two (potentially null) objects.
PatternExpansive
A VeinMiningPattern implementation that "expands" to search for similar blocks.
PatternRegistry
A registry to register any custom implementations of VeinMiningPattern.
PatternThorough
A VeinMiningPattern implementation that "pulsates" from the origin outwards.
PatternUtils
Utility methods for VeinMiningPattern implementations.
PlayerPreferences
Represents a wrapped Player instance holding player-specific data.
PlayerVeinMineEvent
Called when VeinMiner is activated for a set of blocks.
ReflectionUtil  
StatTracker
Represents a statistic tracker for the bStats Metrics class.
ToolCategory
Represents a category of tools recognized by VeinMiner.
ToolTemplate
Represents a template for a ToolCategory's vein mining tool.
ToolTemplateItemStack
A ToolTemplate validated against an ItemStack and its ItemMeta
ToolTemplateMaterial
A ToolTemplate validated against a Material with any meta.
UpdateChecker
A utility class to assist in checking for updates for plugins uploaded to SpigotMC.
UpdateChecker.UpdateReason
A constant reason for the result of UpdateChecker.UpdateResult.
UpdateChecker.VersionScheme
A functional interface to compare two version Strings with similar version schemes.
VaultBasedEconomyModifier
An implementation of EconomyModifier to make use of a Vault-supported economy plugin.
VBlockFace
Represents all possible relative directions of a block supported by VeinMiner.
VeinBlock
Represents a block that may be vein mined.
VeinMiner  
VeinMinerManager
The central management for VeinMiner to handle everything regarding VeinMiner and its features.
VeinMiningPattern
Represents a mining algorithm capable of allocating which blocks should be broken by VeinMiner when a successful vein mine occurs.
